<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="ATA63">
<l>vaṭivuṭaiya ceṅkatirkku māṟāyp pakalē</l>
<l>neṭitulavi niṉṟeṟikkuṅ kollō - kaṭiyulavu</l>
<l>coṉmuṭivoṉ ṟillāta cōtiyāy collāyā</l>
<l>ṉiṉmuṭimē ṟiṅka ṇilā</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Being the opposite of the shapely [one with] red beams, will it</l>
<l>move about long into the day [and] shine constantly, tell [me],</l>
<l>as the light that is without conclusion in words, that goes to protect,</l>
<l>– the light of the moon on your crown?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
